So when taking measurements they USED to be asked if the face is male or female, because you know, biology averages by .5mm difference in facial dimensions, and eye placement with a lens is really important.

Well they've got a SUPER WOKE AF coworker who doesn't believe in biology or that men and women are actually different. She would one day say "everyone who walks in the door today is a man" and take that note with her measurements. Now the years of data they were useless because she was arbitrarily selecting genders.

Now the company has completely done away with genders and everyone is on a universal "average" which has seen an increase in returns and troubleshooting. But at least it's woke, right?
